185
00:10:35,161 --> 00:10:39,443
knew so much about the hostile workplaces and crunch and those problems in the industry

186
00:10:39,483 --> 00:10:42,105
knowing that they would need mental health support there.

187
00:10:42,652 --> 00:10:44,913
And then of course we know in gaming communities too,

188
00:10:44,994 --> 00:10:46,375
there's a lot of in-game harassment

189
00:10:46,415 --> 00:10:47,736
and harassment in gaming communities.

190
00:10:48,176 --> 00:10:49,677
And so we prepared for all of that.

